; zone_custom_params (OSS-03 §7.1): every draft private-use SVCB parameter
; key65400-65405 (cap, cap-sha256, bap, policy, realm, sig) on one record,
; for round-trip tests (R-CORE-3). key65401 reuses the digest of
; testdata/capdoc_chat.json so the zone stays internally consistent.
$ORIGIN example.com.
$TTL 300

_index._agents TXT "agents=booking:mcp"

booking SVCB 1 mcp.example.com. alpn="mcp" port=443 key65400="https://mcp.example.com/.well-known/agent-cap.json" key65401="U0_t8vmbVaTHEXJ3PlnaJNSNvNnfhwOcTZ3WUfJOkbg" key65402="mcp/1,a2a/1" key65403="https://example.com/agent-policy" key65404="production" key65405="c2lnLXBsYWNlaG9sZGVy"
booking TXT  "capabilities=booking,scheduling" "version=3.0.0"
